criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Females who are diagnosed with endometrial carcinoma;

          2. Patients who are willing to receive primary non-reserved fertility function surgery to
             treat their disease;

          3. Patients who are agreed to participated in this prospective cohort study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients who still have the will to have pregnancy;

          2. Patients who have other diseases or heavy injuries that will interfere with the
             results;

          3. Simultaneous participation in another clinical study with investigational medicinal
             product(s) or researcher thinks the subjects are not suitable for this trial.
